							<a href='?src=\ref[src];refresh=rebuild'>Rebuild Lists</a> <a href='?src=\ref[src];refresh=interface'>Refresh</a> <a href='?src=\ref[src];filter=1'>Filtering: [filter_active_only ? "Only Complete" : "All"]</a><br>
